{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"彼岸花开开彼岸","author":"lanxxg"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f0b4646a-c106-50f2-acde-d962fafbcfaf","excerpt":"喜欢听着雨声入睡的夜晚，也喜欢听着雨声醒来的早晨，尤其是周末，这种感觉简直太微微微妙了呀。可是，长时间下雨又会让我感觉不安，甚至焦虑，可能在生活中表现不出来，但内心确实是这样的。还好，这两天总算天晴啦。   前些天使用 Gatsby 和其官方提供的模板 Gatsby blog starter…","html":"<p>喜欢听着雨声入睡的夜晚，也喜欢听着雨声醒来的早晨，尤其是周末，这种感觉简直太微微微妙了呀。可是，长时间下雨又会让我感觉不安，甚至焦虑，可能在生活中表现不出来，但内心确实是这样的。还好，这两天总算天晴啦。  </p>\n<p>前些天使用<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\">Gatsby</a>和其官方提供的模板<a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-blog\">Gatsby blog starter</a>搭建了此网站。希望自己可以在这里写点什么，也许可以坚持很长一段时间，也许会不了了之，不过这一刻我的确想做这件事（手动认真脸）。  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-prismjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber 0\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-prismjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Hello World","date":"March 11, 2019","description":"One thing I wanna do."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/hello-world/","previous":null,"next":null}}